‘Vibrant Summer’ - Live Now.

A ‘chance’ encounter in LA blossomed into a striking new collaboration. We met artist & fashion designer Bradley Baumkirchner and were immediately captivated by his bold, expressive work.

Inspired by his signature floral motifs we knew we had to bring his artistry into the world of Topshop. 

‘Vibrant Summer’ is a limited-edition capsule collection available to shop now.
